7, "blob_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/blob/bb27781b64162e1769df15e0c97e8d2145d2d10d/libstdc%2B%2B-v3%2FChangeLog", "raw_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/raw/bb27781b64162e1769df15e0c97e8d2145d2d10d/libstdc%2B%2B-v3%2FChangeLog", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/contents/libstdc%2B%2B-v3%2FChangeLog?ref=bb27781b64162e1769df15e0c97e8d2145d2d10d", "patch": "@@ -1,3 +1,10 @@\n+2020-05-04  Jonathan Wakely  <jwakely@redhat.com>\n+\n+\tPR libstdc++/94906\n+\t* src/c++17/memory_resource.cc\n+\t(monotonic_buffer_resource::_Chunk::release): Use size_t for shift\n+\toperands.\n+\n 2020-05-04  Nathan Sidwell  <nathan@acm.org>\n \n \tPR libstdc++/94747"}, {"sha": "95352b2353780da158b3715989526bc100ae1614", "filename": "libstdc++-v3/src/c++17/memory_resource.cc", "status": "modified", "additions": 2, "deletions": 2, "changes": 4, "blob_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/blob/bb27781b64162e1769df15e0c97e8d2145d2d10d/libstdc%2B%2B-v3%2Fsrc%2Fc%2B%2B17%2Fmemory_resource.cc", "raw_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/raw/bb27781b64162e1769df15e0c97e8d2145d2d10d/libstdc%2B%2B-v3%2Fsrc%2Fc%2B%2B17%2Fmemory_resource.cc", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/contents/libstdc%2B%2B-v3%2Fsrc%2Fc%2B%2B17%2Fmemory_resource.cc?ref=bb27781b64162e1769df15e0c97e8d2145d2d10d", "patch": "@@ -228,8 +228,8 @@ namespace pmr\n \t  if (__ch->_M_canary != (__ch->_M_size | __ch->_M_align))\n \t    return; // buffer overflow detected!\n \n-\t  size_t __size = (1u << __ch->_M_size);\n-\t  size_t __align = (1u << __ch->_M_align);\n+\t  size_t __size = (size_t)1 << __ch->_M_size;\n+\t  size_t __align = (size_t)1 << __ch->_M_align;\n \t  void* __start = (char*)(__ch + 1) - __size;\n \t  __r->deallocate(__start, __size, __align);\n \t}"}]}